{"tid":1358822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持以暴制暴，但目標要明確，否則只會失民心","createTime":"2019-07-24T04:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T05:19:48.000Z","uid":3432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aec565dc4c8e1d7c6a20dce22799165eb8657482","tid":1358822,"uid":3432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:08:39.000Z","msg":"本人支持以暴制暴，大家都明白和理非對佢地係冇用。<br />\n<br />\n但而家咁多人憎班白衫係因為佢地當晚無差別咁打，我地唔可以同佢地一樣。所以如果我地要報仇，就要起佢地果班白衫打，針對班鄉黑，目標要明確。<br />\n<br />\n目標其實唔係南邊圍，佢地當晚係果到集結只係因為果到近西鐵站又有大空地，我地星期六圍/燒果到其實無用，當白衫根本唔係住果到。<br />\n<br />\n我地星期六應係目標要明確，係要共官鄉警黑勾結，保護元朗村屋，淨化元朗，同時繼續五大訴求。"},{"pid":"46ad0ee10f92a9402d0a1e7e8276bf5b711dbe9a","tid":1358822,"uid":3432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:21:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e92f3ba2dc9bb017e5be27845b7fab2de1697f1","tid":1358822,"uid":3432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:21:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f03b1961748b31bbed61b4c320cc712ad580b56","tid":1358822,"uid":3432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2310a17448357fbf500ed85179f5e950e3a90da2","tid":1358822,"uid":3432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:36:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"61cd120b7d7415132bfbb5716a84e8b8a6f0694e","tid":1358822,"uid":3432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c10affaef6402b593f79a223183884051353b197","tid":1358822,"uid":3432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:19:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0153dbebfc5996bc749ce17451f49ce80a06ce71","tid":1358822,"uid":3432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"推"}]}